    <p class="tools">
              <a href="..\/images\/54906_1858568.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-94529"><strong>View</strong> enlargement</a><br />
                          <a href="http://www.artic.edu/aic/collections/exhibitions/IrvingPennArchives/artwork/94529/email"><strong>Email</strong> to a friend</a><br />
